node.text: "It's a number one priority for individuals with autism to have a site that caters to their individual needs." @eaglesautism  provided a sensory-friendly environment and vaccinations for 1,000 individuals with autism, their caregivers, and families on Saturday at Lincoln Financial Field.

node.title: Eagles Autism Foundation Provides Sensory-Friendly Vaccine Clinic
